Symbols pay anywhere on the screen. The total number of the same symbol on the screen at the end of a spin determines the value of the win.

This is the SCATTER symbol.
SCATTER symbol is present on all reels.
SCATTER pays on any posrtion.

The TUMBLE FEATURE means that after every spin, winning combinations are paid and all winning
symbols disappear. The remaining symbols fall to the bottom of the screen and the empty positions are
replaced with symbols coming from above.
Tumbling will continue until no more winning combinations appear as a result of a tumble.
There's no limit to the number of possible tumbles.

All wins are added to the player's balance after all of the tumbles resulted from a base spin have been played.

This is the multiplier symbol. It is present on all reels and can hit randomly during spins and
tumbles in both base game and FREE SPINS.
Whenever a MULTIPLIER symbol hits, it takes a random multiplier value from 2x to 100x.
When the tumbling sequence ends, the values of all MULTIPLIER symbols on the screen are added
together and the total win of the sequence is multiplied by the final value.

The FREE SPINS FEATURE is awarded when 4 or more SCATTER symbols hit anywhere on the screen.
Hit 4, 5, or 6 SCATTER symbols to trigger 10, 15 or 20 free spins respectively.
The FREE SPINS round has a progressive feature. It starts from level 1 and every time multiplier symbols hit, they are collected in a meter, the round levels up at certain thresholds and in each level only certain values are possible for multiplier symbols,as follows:
Level 1 -Before 6 MULTIPLIER symbols are collected.In level 1,MULTIPLIER symbols can hit from 2x to 100x.
Level 2 -Starts after 6 MULTIPLIER symbols are collected.In level 2,MULTIPLIER symbols can hit from 8x to 100x.
Level 3 -Starts after another 5 MULTIPLIER symbols are collected.In level 3,MULTIPLIER symbols can hit from 15x to 100x.
Level 4 -Starts after another 4 MULTIPLIER symbols are collected.In level 4,MULTIPLIER symbols can hit from 50x to 100x. After level 4 it is not possible to level up anymore and all subsequent free spins are played in level 4.
Whenever 3 or more SCATTER symbols hit during the FREE SPINS ROUND, 5 additional free spins are awarded.
Special reels are in play during the FREE SPINS feature.

The maximum win amount is limited to 5,000x bet. If the total win of a round reaches 5,000x bet
the round immediately ends, win is awarded and all remaining features are forfeited.
